the opportunity to practice demo classes on real students who are learning English.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-1080x762.jpg\" alt=\"teach english online\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"317\" alt=\"teach english online\" class=\"wp-image-59833 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-1080x762.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-800x564.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-450x317.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-163x115.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-255x180.jpg 255w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-768x542.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-1024x722.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-1440x1016.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3-600x423.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07094210\/teach-english-online3.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\