ools. Make sure you have all the documents you need printed out before you go traveling (degree certificate, TEFL certificate, resume) or that you have access to them digitally.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"teach english online\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"teach english online\" class=\"wp-image-59855 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-online8-2-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/07103747\/teach-english-o