n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tefl.org\/tefl-jobs-centre\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">The TEFL Jobs Centre<\/a><\/li><li>Dave&#x2019;s ESL Cafe<\/li><li>ESL Job Feed<\/li><li>TEFL Jobs World<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great way to search for jobs is through Facebook groups in your chosen country. There are many Facebook communities for teachers, where you can post an advert or search for jobs.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-make-money-online\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">14 amazing online jobs and where to find them!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-how-much-do-i-make-by-teaching-english\">How much do I make by teaching English? <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to this, teaching English can pay well too. Those that teach in places like South Korea or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Vietnam<\/a> can save a lot of money! This can then be put towards your travels while you teach English Abroad.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Learn:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/become-digital-nomad\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to live a life as a digital nomad and make money online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-cost-of-living-and-salary\">Cost of Living and Salary<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to research the average salary rate for an English teacher, and how far your money will go in that country. For instance, countries like Vietnam pay very well for English teachers and the cost of living is extremely low. Because of this, it&#x2019;s a favorite among TEFL teachers. Additionally, it&#x2019;s in a great location to explore the rest of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/asia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asia<\/a>! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, in countries like Japan, the pay may be good but the cost of living is very expensive. In these situations, look for other job perks like free accommodation.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Why teach English? Teaching requirements Best TEFL courses How to find a job? Why Choose to Teach English? Anybody can have their own reasons for why she or he would like to start teaching English. The simple answer would be that it brings you many new opportunities. Reasons to teach English can be to: Learn [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":59837,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","